data.title: My Village at Sunset
data.meta_description: My Village at Sunset is a 1992 Cambodian romantic drama film directed by Norodom Sihanouk. After the 1991 peace agreements, a handsome, young Cambodian doctor returns from Paris to volunteer his services at a clinic in his home village in rural Cambodia, just outside the capital city.
